{"tid":2363423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FB大清洗｜拜登就職前「洗太平地」 Twitter刪7萬陰謀論賬戶 馬斯克斥審查打擊言論自由","createTime":"2021-01-12T07:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T11:57:49.000Z","uid":37808,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"17901dfce2d2110ccd68333134a5d1e363902e4a","tid":2363423,"uid":37808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"Facebook和Twitter等主流社交媒體大舉封殺美國總統特朗普及其支持者的賬戶，惹來審查言論和妨礙言論自由的質疑。不過，Facebook繼續為美國總統當選人拜登的就職典禮鋪路，Facebook周一宣佈，會移除所有包含「Stop the steal」（停止竊取選舉，特朗普以此形容大選結果被竊.........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主流社交媒體Facebook和Twitter大舉封殺特朗普和其支持者賬戶，蘋果、Google和亞馬遜再聯手打壓保守派的新社交媒體平台Parler，惹來各界關注。<strong><span class=\"red\">Tesla創辦人馬斯克（Elon Musk）便在Twitter轉發保守派媒體Babylon Bee的文章。該文章形容科網巨企的審查行徑是「邪惡法西斯式獨裁者」，而馬斯克則留言稱，很多人對於這些科技公司充當起自由言論的實際仲裁人，將感到非常不高興。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210112/F2N2ACZJDZANDHWQZ44BVUMK3E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0hBAygehgLoWz-6DHDS76FQY3QpR02rFSzXKtz0IPjoeG6WusXCAUnFhg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210112%2FF2N2ACZJDZANDHWQZ44BVUMK3E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0hBAygehgLoWz-6DHDS76FQY3QpR02rFSzXKtz0IPjoeG6WusXCAUnFhg&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJuTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=91c5036b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210112%2FF2N2ACZJDZANDHWQZ44BVUMK3E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0hBAygehgLoWz-6DHDS76FQY3QpR02rFSzXKtz0IPjoeG6WusXCAUnFhg&h=99f000c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210112/F2N2ACZJDZANDHWQZ44BVUMK3E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_sour